<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6361661>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12–15. Anthroherpon spelaebatoides Noesske, 1914. 12: pronotum, ventral aspect, scale bar 0.70 mm; 13: mesono- tum—scutum, scutellum, metanotum, scale bar 0.44 mm; 14: venter, scale bar 0.70 mm; 15: mesothorax, right latero–ventral aspect, without scale bar." ;
