<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6361663>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16–21. 16: Anthroherpon cylindricollis cylindricollis Apfelbeck, 1889, venter, without scale bar, 17: mesothorax, right latero–ventral aspect, without scale bar; 18: Anthroherpon zariquieyi Jeannel, 1930, venter, without scale bar; 19: Anthroherpon primitivum primitivum Absolon, 1913, venter, without scale bar, 20: mesothorax, right latero–ventral aspect, without scale bar; 21: Anthroherpon piesbergeni Zariquiey, 1927, venter, without scale bar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6361663/files/figure.png" ;
