<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6361655>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2–5. 2: Anthroherpon cylindricollis cylindricollis Apfelbeck, 1889, scale bar 4.3 mm. 3: Anthroherpon zariquieyi Jeannel, 1930, scale bar 3.8 mm. 4: Anthroherpon primitivum primitivum Absolon, 1913, scale bar 4.5 mm. 5: Anthroherpon piesbergeni Zariquiey, 1927, scale bar 4.6 mm. All originals by D. Beňo, ex Hlaváč, Perreau & Čeplík 2017." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6361655/files/figure.png" ;
