<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6361667>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22–27. Mesoventral process. 22: Anthroherpon cylindricollis cylindricollis Apfelbeck, 1889; 23: Anthroherpon hossei Winkler, 1925; 24: Anthroherpon piesbergeni Zariquiey, 1927; 25: Anthroherpon primitivum primitivum Absolon, 1913; 26: Anthroherpon stenocephalum stenocephalum Apfelbeck, 1901; 27: Anthroherpon zariquieyi Jeannel, 1930." ;
