<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6361669>
    dc:description "FIGURES 28–32. Anthroherpon spelaebatoides Noesske, 1914: 28: metendosternite, dorsal aspect, scale bar 0.95 mm, 29: aedeagus, dorsal aspect, scale bar 0.46 mm, 30: median lobe, right lateral aspect, scale bar 0.34 mm, 31: spermatheca, scale bar 0.08 mm; 32: Anthroherpon cylindricollis cylindricollis Apfelbeck, 1889, spermatheca, scale bar 0.19 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6361669/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6361673>
    dc:description "FIGURES 33–37. Anthroherpon spelaebatoides Noesske, 1914: 33: female sternite VIII, dorsal aspect, scale bar 0.56 mm; 34: female sternite IX, dorsal aspect, scale bar 0.23 mm. Spelaeobates novaki Müller, 1901: 35: pronotum, right lateral aspect, without scale bar; 36: scape and pedicel, without scale bar; 37: left maxilla, dorsal aspect, without scale bar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6361673/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6361675>
